OL,3,CHigh cost of living 'main reason' for
OL,4,CJersey's low birth rate
OL,6,FProspective parents in Jersey say the
OL,7,Fhigh cost of living is the main reason
OL,8,Fwhy the island has one of the lowest
OL,9,Fbirth rates in Europe.
OL,11,FThe number of actual births in 2023
OL,12,Fwas under 800, the lowest in almost 70
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FMother-of-two Natalie Fosse tells ITV
OL,16,FNews that she put off having her
OL,17,Fsecond child until her first was of
OL,18,Fschool age due to the soaring cost of
OL,19,Fchildcare.
