OL,3,CHigh cost of living 'main reason' for
OL,4,CJersey's low birth rate
OL,6,FShe explains: "People need help, they
OL,7,Fneed support and they are not getting
OL,8,Fit.
OL,10,F"The system has never really worked
OL,11,Fover here, help is definitely needed
OL,12,Ffor mums and dads."
OL,14,FNelson Santos has a daughter and a
OL,15,Fstepson and believes the high cost of
OL,16,Fhousing is putting people off having
OL,17,Fmore children.
OL,19,FHe says: "It's really sad because
OL,20,Fbeing a parent is the best thing that
OL,21,Fcould have happened for me.
