OL,4,CJersey's low birth rate
OL,6,F"There are many factors that can have
OL,7,Fan effect on the birth rate including
OL,8,Fpersonal preference, cost of living
OL,9,Fand migration.
OL,11,F"We also know that islanders have good
OL,12,Flevels of sex and sexual health
OL,13,Feducation which can reduce the number
OL,14,Fof unplanned pregnancies."
